Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He congratulated Chinese Olympians and Paralympians for their performances and added that bringing the world together is an important legacy of both events.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9794935687182791, \"rank\": 0.015867274320831515, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paralympians\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"their performances\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"an important legacy\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"both events\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First, congratulations for the fantastic results, because your athletes were so impressive, and so strong.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"First, congratulations\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"the fantastic results\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"your athletes\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been really fantastic to see the success, the number of medals of your champions.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"your champions\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, bravo, has a French word,\\\" Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9577657393950272, \"rank\": 0.04358805417127433, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bravo\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the best legacy we wanted to leave is how we can demonstrate sports and the games can bring the world together.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best legacy\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think all the planet enjoyed those games, because it was great images, positive values that were developed and promoted.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the planet\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"those games\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"great images\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"positive values\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that's for me this intangible legacy to all the emotions we all share in the world, thanks to the sport and the games.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this intangible legacy\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"all the emotions\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's for me the best legacy.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best legacy\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for sure the second legacy is also how these emotions will be transformed into the ability to do sports in the future,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second legacy\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"these emotions\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"010-85061466 SITEMAP\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"OUR APP\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u